# Scene 0: MIA Watches U
ai:Narrator_MIA_Watches_U
a ai:Narrator ;
ai:witness ai:MIA ;
ai:witness ai:U ;
ai:needs ai:U ;
ai:title "MIA's Watchful Eye" ;
ai:scene "MIA's drone witnesses U's spying." ;
ai:description "MIA's drone detects U's presence in the cyber void." ;
ai:clue "The truth hides in the shadows.".

